605
00:33:17,660 --> 00:33:18,820
that I was practicing Ice Spirit in the back mountain

606
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,100
last night?

607
00:33:22,380 --> 00:33:23,380
So,

608
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:25,620
