609
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:28,300
Has Liu Shao been in the back mountain for the past three days?

610
00:33:28,300 --> 00:33:29,460
Of course.

611
00:33:29,460 --> 00:33:30,780
She never left.

612
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:33,020
If it wasn't because

613
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:34,620
