615
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:39,060
and then brought it to Immortal herself.

616
00:33:44,300 --> 00:33:44,900
Immortal.

617
00:33:45,660 --> 00:33:46,260
Immortal?

618
00:33:47,220 --> 00:33:47,780
Immortal?

