622
00:33:57,500 --> 00:33:57,980
Well...

623
00:33:59,140 --> 00:33:59,820
What's wrong?

624
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:10,900
Luo Ge.

625
00:34:11,580 --> 00:34:12,739
I just want to ask you,

626
00:34:13,580 --> 00:34:14,620
