627
00:34:24,139 --> 00:34:24,739
Sorry.

628
00:34:25,980 --> 00:34:26,659
I'm late.

629
00:34:29,340 --> 00:34:30,340
Immortal Luo Ge.

630
00:34:30,340 --> 00:34:31,250
What are you doing?

631
00:34:31,500 --> 00:34:32,380
Wan Sui proved

632
00:34:32,739 --> 00:34:34,540
