Immortal,

642
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:05,290
Palace Wuxie has its own rules.

643
00:35:05,740 --> 00:35:07,780
Since Liu Shao has been handed over to Palace Wuxie for execution,

644
00:35:08,020 --> 00:35:09,060
