645
00:35:24,780 --> 00:35:25,300
Luo Ge,

646
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:28,340
even if you enter the depths of her nightmare now,

647
00:35:28,700 --> 00:35:30,060
I'm afraid there's nothing you can do.

648
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:31,900
You might not be able to come back too.

649
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:18,540
Liu Shao.

650
00:36:31,210 --> 00:36:32,890
Liu Shao, wake up.

651
00:36:34,540 --> 00:36:35,780
Do you remember me?

652
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:36,260
Liu Shao.

653
00:36:36,260 --> 00:36:37,220
We either die together...

654
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:38,020
I'm Luo Ge.

655
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:39,300
or we go together.

656
00:36:41,730 --> 00:36:42,780
We either die together...

657
00:36:55,140 --> 00:36:57,340
Don't... don't leave me!

658
00:36:57,340 --> 00:36:58,780
Liu Shao, wake up!

659
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:00,900
Do you know

660
00:37:01,220 --> 00:37:02,300
that you will become a nightmare,

661
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:03,780
