662
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:05,860
Let me go!

663
00:37:06,460 --> 00:37:07,380
Let go of me!

664
00:37:32,860 --> 00:37:33,700
Lu Li.

665
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:35,220
Why are you here?

666
00:37:36,700 --> 00:37:37,610
Luo Ge.

667
00:37:38,250 --> 00:37:39,180
Let me ask you one last time,

668
00:37:40,130 --> 00:37:41,060
