676
00:37:55,540 --> 00:37:57,380
Lu Li died, all of this is fake.

677
00:37:58,180 --> 00:37:58,780
This is not a dream,

678
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,140
I'm real.

679
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:07,310
♫The reflection gradually reminded me of our first meeting♫

680
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,340
The real Luo Ge

681
00:38:05,700 --> 00:38:06,740
and the real Lu Li.

682
00:38:08,010 --> 00:38:13,200
♫I can no longer tell the difference between wind and rain♫

683
00:38:14,410 --> 00:38:18,050
♫Even if I get the volley sword♫

684
00:38:17,930 --> 00:38:18,780
Luo Ge?

685
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:22,070
♫I can't forget you♫

686
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:25,660
♫Our destiny has been sealed long ago♫

687
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,020
Luo Ge.

688
00:38:24,260 --> 00:38:25,340
I don't want to leave.

689
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:27,610
